<span id="freeTextContainer3330534433781210969">This is a book that needs time to ponder, percolate, and wonder. Sometimes it gets rather thick and then I needed to reread. <a href='https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/8052.Pema_Ch_dr_n' title='Pema Chödrön' rel='nofollow noopener'>Pema Chödrön</a> guides you to think about yourself and what scares you and she also has you go outside of yourself and think of people you care for and people you don&apos;t care for and those you do not know. I&apos;m glad I bought this book because it is full of highlights that I will refer back to for a long time to come.</span>
