        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1167896537" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer6655930076493783431">I have started reading this book three times and only the third time managed to finish it. Not because it is one of those boring books that one has to force themselves through. Not at all. But because it is a special kind of book that needs a special state of mind. It took me almost one year to find that state of mind and get back to reading it. Although I suspect I just can put it on read and leave it aside. I wish to keep it on my special shelf on my library, the shelf of books that I consult </span>
  <span id="freeText6655930076493783431" style="display:none">I have started reading this book three times and only the third time managed to finish it. Not because it is one of those boring books that one has to force themselves through. Not at all. But because it is a special kind of book that needs a special state of mind. It took me almost one year to find that state of mind and get back to reading it. Although I suspect I just can put it on read and leave it aside. I wish to keep it on my special shelf on my library, the shelf of books that I consult from time to time and from which I constantly learn something new.<br /></span>
